	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This depends on OS, the exact set of video modes available, and the exact details of Nestopia's video implementation.<br /><br />For me, on linux, I added a bunch of explicitly specified video modes to get full vertical size on my 16:9 monitors.<br /><br />Also, what version are you using?<br /><br />It looks like you're still using 1.4.0—you might see if the newer version changes anything mentioned here: <!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10047">viewtopic.php?t=10047</a><!-- l -->

		

