	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />At 720p, you want 3x. If there are black borders on the top and bottom, those represent the area traditionally covered by overscan. Some HDTVs cut off the top and bottom lines of component or HDMI input, just as they do composite. What resolution are you using?

		

		</td>
